# bin/ holds the suite's COPIED `auths-mcp-gateway` build artifact, staged by the
# suite rebuild (cargo build --release -p auths-mcp-gateway, then copied here).
# The gateway probes content-hash it against target/release/auths-mcp-gateway; it
# is reproducible, so it is not committed. Same convention as the other suites'
# bin/.
*
!.gitignore
